000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aoeC4Uj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaoeC4Uj.gif&h=e390aa5a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aoeC4Uj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaoeC4Uj.gif&h=e390aa5a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aoeC4Uj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaoeC4Uj.gif&h=e390aa5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d07ed71b5cc86056240897e892e62fb3f59bf2f2","tid":1662990,"uid":185158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:22:06.000Z","msg":"證明香港政研會係支持劉曉波！"},{"pid":"96266d366f0ecb81b4e0cd5102d5b6b8522c521c","tid":1662990,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:28:21.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"a25e428a37dc6af0aefd674fdc63b5bd7e637759","tid":1662990,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:29:26.000Z","msg":"包攬化學數學獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有得諗"},{"pid":"73dfc12dd1139185621586a6806591da82492cca","tid":1662990,"uid":61032,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:40:56.000Z","msg":"醫學獎：全身100%燒傷個案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}